y":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T11:20:44.000Z","msg":"近乎0 latency<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 瞓醒未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:42:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Tmymvvs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTmymvvs.png&h=27c9fbc9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1ms"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:50:11.000Z","msg":"理論同實綫有距離㗎"},{"pid":"d8704991ff490993fc6f8afbf5b6cc51e7106400","tid":1096700,"uid":8257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94f2abec7ed6b538d3e416f4fbeedbc24ab29f6c","tid":1096700,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T01:30:17.000Z","msg":"港媒稱，韓國搶先推出商業5G服務，屬全球第一。美國也緊隨其後，電訊商Verizon預定於11日推出5G服務，但現時真正<span style=\"color: red;\">支持5G網絡</span>的手機僅有三星<strong>Galaxy S10 5G</strong>，而美國威瑞森電信公司的行貨要待至下半年才推出，可能出現&ldquo;<span style=\"color: green;\">有5G網但無機用</span>&rdquo;的尷尬局面。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gulfnews.com/201904/S10%20release%20Korea_resources1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gulfnews.com%2F201904%2FS10%2520release%2520Korea_resources1.jpg&h=9c303537&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《香港經濟日報》網站4月4日報道，威瑞森在接下來的一周將率先在芝加哥和明尼阿波利斯推出5G服務，網絡速度最高1Gbps，為現時4G LTE網絡的10倍速度。該公司還計劃在今年內推展至美國超過30個城市。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.pocket-lint.com/r/s/1200x/assets/images/147622-phones-news-samsung-galaxy-s10-5g-available-from-5-april-image1-nxgzjgoamv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.pocket-lint.com%2Fr%2Fs%2F1200x%2Fassets%2Fimages%2F147622-phones-news-samsung-galaxy-s10-5g-available-from-5-april-image1-nxgzjgoamv.jpg&h=ad8c4bbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報道稱，5G手機款式不足卻意外地成為問題。全球首款支援5G的手機為三星Galaxy S10 5G，近日在韓國推出，美國用戶要多等一季，因為這款手機將由威瑞森率先獨家發售，但行貨今年下半年才開賣，其余電信商AT&amp;T、T-Mobile和Sprint更要年底才有貨。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/4006/4006707.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F4006%2F4006707.jpg&h=cdd28bba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n除了三星，摩托羅拉 Z3亦能夠支援5G，但預定8月才推出。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/Kud53N0Evoc/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FKud53N0Evoc%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=7ca37782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n報道指出，威瑞森成為第一家在美國推出5G網絡的電信商，T-Mobile和Sprint則計劃於今年稍後才提供5G服務，或許可以避免&ldquo;有網無機用&rdquo;的情況。但據報道，這兩家企業至今仍未啟動其5G網絡。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T12:53:56.000Z","msg":"美國5G而家係畀屋企上網用喎 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"925d5be4ac4e05f0faed7e2d3be2b245c40d3d2c","tid":1096700,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcd999526e895799ca25a0aa8730968edc2cda2d","tid":1096700,"uid":130901,"like":14,"dislike":17,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"9cf1ae1ff8887dfce621fdc4139c1bc119352d91","tid":1096700,"uid":99885,"like":28,"dislike":5,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"dfadd9e7c6358dcacd0136f43d328fa4a6301fa0","tid":1096700,"uid":130901,"like":4,"dislike":19,"score":-15,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T02:21:45.000Z","msg":"吹到5G咁勁，聽完覺得手機並唔需要由4G升上5G<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T03:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dA8gErg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdA8gErg.png&h=ca6bb98e&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-08T03:37:41.000Z","msg":"咪懶風趣啦<br />\n<br />\n56K轉寛頻 同 4G轉5G無得比較"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T13:08:18.000Z","msg":"坐咗幾耐定真心膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7b1e12c22da6